  <brief_title>Sublingual Administration of PPI</brief_title>
  <official_title>Sublingual Administration is More Fast Than Oral or IV Administration in PPI Dosing With Respect to Intragastric pH and Therapeutic Effectiveness: a Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
